SQL Question

Employee table:

emp_id	emp_name	salary	department

Write SQL query to fetch:

employee name
salary
rank of employee within their department based on salary

Expected concepts:

DENSE_RANK()
PARTITION BY
-------------------------------------------------
SELECT
    emp_name,
    salary,
    department,
    DENSE_RANK() OVER (
        PARTITION BY department
        ORDER BY salary DESC
    ) AS dept_rank
FROM Employee;